The generator should:
1. Replace the parameterized constructor with a parameterless one that sets default values
2. Change `owner` to `private _owner` 
3. Update `whitelistUser` to reset the mint counter on removal (with status change check)
4. Cache `preSaleWalletMinted[msg.sender]` in `mintTokenWhitelisted`

